description: Titan NRG Inc., through its subsidiaries, operates as a downstream energy and transportation company in the United States. The company operates 25 transports in 9 states. It offers retail and commercial propane through approximately 1500 leased tanks in southern Arizona; engages in the wholesale purchase and sale of LPG products; and has a long-term lease on 18 car rail facility with approved 1.2 mm gallons of propane/butane storage in Tucson. The company was founded in 2001 and is based in Tucson, Arizona.
